  "faq": {
    "title": "Frequently asked questions",
    "q1Q": "How does SKOLZ work?",
    "q1A": "SKOLZ connects qualified experts with clients who need advice. Browse profiles, choose an expert, book a slot, and pay online. Sessions are held via video link.",
    "q2Q": "How do I become an expert on SKOLZ?",
    "q2A": "Sign up with the \"Expert\" role, create your profile, and set your availability. Our team reviews your application before approving it.",
    "q3Q": "How are rates calculated?",
    "q3A": "Each expert sets their own hourly rate. The final price depends on the chosen session duration. Discounts may apply via promo codes or gift cards.",
    "q4Q": "How does payment work?",
    "q4A": "Payments are processed securely via Stripe. You pay at booking, and the expert receives payment after the session.",
    "q5Q": "Can I cancel a booking?",
    "q5A": "Yes, you can cancel a booking from your dashboard. See our refund policy for applicable conditions.",
    "q6Q": "Are experts verified?",
    "q6A": "All expert profiles are reviewed by our team before activation. For regulated fields (law, medicine), a professional license reference is required.",
    "q7Q": "How do I leave a review?",
    "q7A": "After a completed session, you can leave a 5-star rating with a comment from your booking page.",
    "q8Q": "How do I contact support?",
    "q8A": "Go to your dashboard > Support to open a ticket. Our team responds within 24 to 48 hours."
  },
